    • isAuthorized

      public static <A extends org.apache.fulcrum.security.model.turbine.TurbineAccessControlList<?>> boolean isAuthorized(AccessibleObject object, A acl)
      Check if the object given is authorized to be executed based on its annotations The method will return false if one of the annotations denies execution
      Typparameter:
      A - ACL instance
      Parameter:
      object - accessible object to test
      acl - access control list
      Gibt zurück:
      true if the execution is allowed

      • isAuthorized(AccessibleObject, TurbineAccessControlList, ConditionType)

    • isAuthorized

      public static <A extends org.apache.fulcrum.security.model.turbine.TurbineAccessControlList<?>> boolean isAuthorized(AccessibleObject object, A acl, AnnotationProcessor.ConditionType conditonType)
      Check if the object given is authorized to be executed based on its annotations The method's return value depends on the conditonType, refer to the ConditionType
      Typparameter:
      A - ACL instance
      Parameter:
      object - the object
      acl - access control list
      conditonType - either AnnotationProcessor.ConditionType.COMPOUND: The method will return false if one of the annotations denies execution or AnnotationProcessor.ConditionType.ANY : The method will return true if one of the annotations allows execution
      Gibt zurück:
      true if the execution is allowed

    • process

      public static void process(Object object, Boolean hasTurbineServicesInMethodFields) throws TurbineException
      Search for annotated fields and optionally of method fields of the object and inject the appropriate objects
      Parameter:
      object - the object
      hasTurbineServicesInMethodFields - set true , if methods should be parsed
      Löst aus:
      TurbineException - if the objects could not be injected
